## Trains

The nearest stations are Matlock and Chesterfield.

## Buses

There are buses to Ashover until early evening on Friday and later to Kelstedge (5 mins drive from Ashover) from Sheffield and Chesterfield.

[Traveline East Midlands](http://www.travelineeastmidlands.co.uk)

## Station pick-ups

We will be organising lifts to Ashover Parish Hall on Friday evening from Matlock and Chesterfield stations and in the opposite direction on Sunday and Monday afternoons. Please [contact us](mailto:skint.dance@gmail.com) with information about your arrival time so we can coordinate this. There will be a small charge for this service to cover fuel costs.

## Car parking

There is plenty of parking next to the venue. Please avoid parking in front of the medical centre.
